          <actionDate>2018-04-19</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Protecting Moms and Infants Act</strong></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2023 the residential substance-use-treatment program&nbsp;for pregnant and postpartum women and requires the Department of Health and Human Services to make recommendations&nbsp;for addressing prenatal opioid use. Further, the Center for Substance Abuse Treatment must develop substance-use-disorder educational materials for treating pregnant women and babies.</p>]]></text>
